article_id:401,category_name:News,title_name:High Mercury's Trial Is Coming Soon to Advanced Dragon Trials!,image_path:,message:<div>High Mercury&#39;s Trial will be added to the Advanced Dragon Trials, the most challenging of event quests, at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1555567200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a9d746598e736ef0e8ce62100de92371.png"></div><div>The Waterwyrm Mercury releases her true powers and becomes High Mercury. Her immense mana acts as a great current that coats her body. With the kindness to protect those she cares for&mdash;and the strength to repel all threats&mdash;she&#39;s a truly wondrous dragon.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. In order to challenge High Mercury&#39;s Trial, a player&#39;s team must have 13,000 might or higher.</div><div>2. Players must have completed Mercury&#39;s Trial: Master to challenge High Mercury&#39;s Trial.</div><div>3. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1555394400,update_time1555306232